HEADWORD: Cuspid
<hw>Cus"pid</hw> <pr>(k⟦ucr⟧s"p⟦icr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Cusp</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>One of the canine teeth;
